Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Disables Windows Ink Workspace and handwriting data collection.
; Collects data on how you type and write to improve Microsoft services.
; WARNING: Skip if you use a stylus or pen input device.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\WindowsInkWorkspace]
"AllowWindowsInkWorkspace"=dword:00000000
